Chairman:CouncilofZhejiangPlasticsEngineeringSociety
Member:ChineseChemicalSociety,AmericanChemicalSociety,AmericanNanoSociety
ZhengpingFangreceivedhisBScdegreein1983fromDepartmentofChemistryatFudanUniversityandMScdegreein1986fromInstituteofMaterialsScienceatFudanUniversity.HejoinedDepartmentofPolymerScienceandEngineeringin1998whenZhejiangUniversitywasmergedwithHangzhouUniversityandothertwouniversities.PriortothathewasaprofessorattheDepartmentofChemistryofHangzhouUniversity.HeisalsoProfessorofNingboInstituteofTechnology,ZhejiangUniversity.HeteachesPolymerPhysicscourseforundergraduateprogramandPolymerSurfaceandInterfacecourseforgraduateprogram.
Hisresearchinterestisinthestructure-propertiesrelationshipofmulti-componentpolymersystemsandthemodificationofpolymericmaterialsviablending,filling,andcompounding.Heandhiscolleaguesdevelopedcompatibilization-crosslinkingsynergismtechniquethatcouldbeusedtoimprovethemechanicalpropertiesofimmisciblepolymerblendswithhighefficiency.Intherecentyears,hisresearchisconcentratedinthedevelopmentofhalogen-freeflameretardantplastics,especiallythosecontainingP-Ncompoundsandnano-fillers.
			
				
			Researchwork
			
